    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Software\" title=\"Software\">Software</a> * <a href=\"/Utilities\" title=\"Utilities\">Utilities</a> * Wb2UCI</b>\n</p><p><b>Wb2UCI</b>, (Wb2Uci, WB2UCI)<br />\na <a href=\"/Protocols\" title=\"Protocols\">protocol</a> adapter by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a> to run <a href=\"/Category:WinBoard\" title=\"Category:WinBoard\">WinBoard Engines</a> using the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> under chess <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUIs</a> supporting <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a>, such as the <a href=\"/Shredder#GUI\" title=\"Shredder\">Shredder GUI</a>. Wb2UCI is a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Console_application\">console application</a> running under <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a>. \nAlong with the executable <b>Wb2Uci.exe</b>, one must place a <b>Wb2Uci.eng</b> textfile into the engine folder <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Wb2Uci.eng\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Wb2Uci.eng</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Engines\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Engines</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#GUIs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">GUIs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Postings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Postings</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2001_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2001 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Wb2Uci.eng\">Wb2Uci.eng</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wb2UCI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Wb2Uci.eng\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>The <b>Wb2Uci.eng</b> file consists of following mandatory <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Attribute%E2%80%93value_pair\">attribute–value pairs</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, and many more optional.\n</p>\n<pre>\n;---------------------------\n[ENGINE]\nName=Name of engine\nAuthor=Name of engine author\nFilename=Wb2Uci.exe\n\n[OPTIONS]\nProgram=engine.exe\n;---------------------------\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Engines\">Engines</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wb2UCI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Engines\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Category:WinBoard\" title=\"Category:WinBoard\">WinBoard Engines</a> </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"GUIs\">GUIs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wb2UCI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: GUIs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/UCI#GUI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI compatible GUIs</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wb2UCI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/InBetween\" title=\"InBetween\">InBetween</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/UCI2WB\" title=\"UCI2WB\">UCI2WB</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Postings\">Postings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wb2UCI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Postings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2001_...\">2001 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wb2UCI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2001 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=33936\">Help - The King; Chessbase/Fritz GUI</a> by John Hatcher, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 10, 2001</li></ul>\n<p><b>2002</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=215566\">UCI2Wb by Odd Gunnar Malin</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_Gemuh\" title=\"Matthias Gemuh\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 26, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI2WB\" title=\"UCI2WB\">UCI2WB</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=36342\">Wb2Uci from Odd Gunnar Malin is working well on Shredder5 GUI</a> by Carlos E.A. Drake, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 06, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Shredder#GUI\" title=\"Shredder\">Shredder GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=218644\">The King and Wb2Uci</a> by Ralph Patriquin, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 19, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/The_King\" title=\"The King\">The King</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=36656\">Wb2uci question</a> by Jouni, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 02, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=36819&amp;p=139614#p139734\">Re: Fritz protocol</a> by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 14, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Fritz\" title=\"Fritz\">Fritz</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=39155\">Wb2Uci</a> by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 23, 2002</li></ul>\n<p><b>2003</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=274600\">Need help with CM 9000 and WB2UCI</a> by Ralph Patriquin, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 02, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Chessmaster\" title=\"Chessmaster\">Chessmaster</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=284077\">Wb2Uci and XP</a> by Chessfun, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=284985\">Re: Can Gandalf 5 be run under Fritz GUI as an UCI engine w/ Wb2UCI&#160;?</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Manfred_Meiler&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Manfred Meiler (page does not exist)\">Manfred Meiler</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 18, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Gandalf\" title=\"Gandalf\">Gandalf</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=41334\">List of 31 not-working engines (Fritz-GUI, XP). Any help?</a> by Surak, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, February 20, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=306801\">wb2uci,eng w comments</a> by <a href=\"/Michael_Byrne\" title=\"Michael Byrne\">Mike Byrne</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 16, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Rebel\" title=\"Rebel\">Rebel</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=43496\">Wb2UCI and Problems with ExChess4.03a and GnuChess4.0.8</a> by <a href=\"/Arturo_Ochoa\" title=\"Arturo Ochoa\">Arturo Ochoa</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, July 24, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/EXchess\" title=\"EXchess\">EXchess</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess\" title=\"GNU Chess\">GNU Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=43805\">Engine Gaviota + WB2UCI in Fritz7 don,t Work pondering</a> by Luis Andraschnik, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, August 15, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Gaviota\" title=\"Gaviota\">Gaviota</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2004</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=45863\">Crafty 19.08 SE 2004 released ...</a> by <a href=\"/Michael_Byrne\" title=\"Michael Byrne\">Michael Byrne</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 01, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=341498\">The King's Wb2UCI file</a> by Darren Rushton, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 10, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/The_King\" title=\"The King\">The King</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=48455\">GLC and others when using wb2uci</a> by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, August 03, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Green_Light_Chess\" title=\"Green Light Chess\">Green Light Chess</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wb2UCI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=407137\">To Odd-Gunnar Malin: Bug in WB2UCI-adaptor</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Franz_Huber&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Franz Huber (page does not exist)\">Franz Huber</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 23, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=431484\">Re: New Wb2Uci 1.3 B21</a> by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 16, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13045\">Where is the latest wb2uci.exe file available from?</a> by <a href=\"/Graham_Banks\" title=\"Graham Banks\">Graham Banks</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 12, 2007 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=19&amp;t=50429\">UCI protocol in winboard</a> by <a href=\"/Engin_%C3%9Cst%C3%BCn\" title=\"Engin Üstün\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 24, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a>, <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a>, <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wb2UCI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32256\">n/s speed of search through Wb2Uci - need some clarification</a> by <a href=\"/Martin_Thoresen\" title=\"Martin Thoresen\">Martin Thoresen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 01, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39426\">Need help reading Arena debug and wb2uci logfiles</a> by <a href=\"/Adam_Hair\" title=\"Adam Hair\">Adam Hair</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 19, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47232\">wb2uci adaptor,where can I get it? please!</a> by markchessman, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51276\">WB2UCI for Java executable chess engines too?</a> by <a href=\"/Norbert_Raimund_Leisner\" title=\"Norbert Raimund Leisner\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 14, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52914\">WB2UCI.EXE adapter</a> by Jim Logan, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 08, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wb2UCI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58982\">wb2uci adapter - different results with different versions</a> by Wilhelm Hudetz, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 20, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60699\">WB2UCI</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Brendan_J._Norman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Brendan J. Norman (page does not exist)\">Brendan J. Norman</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 05, 2016</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wb2UCI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20120515104014/http://home.online.no:80/%7Emalin/sjakk/Wb2Uci/\">Winboard as UCI engine</a> by <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a>, hosted by the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">WaybackMachine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://adamsccpages.blogspot.de/p/computer-chess-utility-programs.html#h\">Adam's Computer Chess Pages: Computer Chess Utility Programs - WB2UCI</a> by <a href=\"/Adam_Hair\" title=\"Adam Hair\">Adam Hair</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://americanfoot.free.fr/echecs/suisse/fichiers.htm\">Le Système du Suisse</a> has wbconf07.zip  with approximately 300 Wb2Uci.eng files </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sourceforge.net/p/craftychessinterface/wiki/wb2uci%20with%20multiple%20engines/\">Crafty Chess Interface / Wiki / wb2uci with multiple engines</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsectio